import Vue from 'vue'
import App from './App.vue'
import router from './router'
import store from './store'

import toast from './components/common/toast'

Vue.config.productionTip = false

// 添加事件总线对象
Vue.prototype.$bus = new Vue()
    // 安装toast插件
Vue.use(toast)

new Vue({
    router,
    store,
    render: h => h(App)
}).$mount('#app')
